    "The main advantage of quantum states prepared by parameterized quantum circuits is an enhanced expressivity when compared to low-rank tensor states that can be classically computed 104, 105.",
    "Expressivity can be measured by investigating how much entanglement entropy Sðρ",
    "of a bipartite system can be efficiently captured by the variational wave function.",
